#. module: corporate_gifts
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:corporate_gifts.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>Then add the product \"B&amp;C Inspire Woman\"</strong></font>, a grid open to select multiple quantities per size. Print the quotation to see how it looks.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>ຈາກນັ້ນເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າ "
"\"B&amp;C Inspire Woman\"</strong></font>, ຕາຕະລາງຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອເລືອກຈຳນວນຫຼາຍລາຍກາ"
"ນຕໍ່ຂະໜາດ. ພິມໃບສະເໜີລາຄາເພື່ອເບິ່ງວ່າຮູບຮ່າງເປັນແນວໃດ.\n"
"            </span>"

#. module: corporate_gifts
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:corporate_gifts.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                This setup is for marketing companies selling and producing customized corporate gifts, like mugs and t-shirts. A typical sale order is a company buying 50 red t-shirts for his employees, customized with their logo on the\n"
"                pocket, with quantities like:  5 Small, 10 Medium, 25 Large, 10 XL.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ແມ່ນສຳລັບບໍລິສັດການຕະຫຼາດທີ່ຂາຍ ແລະ ຜະລິດຂອງຂວັນອົງກອນແບບປັບແຕ່ງເອ"
"ງ ເຊັ່ນ: ຈອກ ແລະ ເສື້ອຢືດ. ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍປົກກະຕິແມ່ນ ບໍລິສັດຊື້ເສື້ອຢືດສີແດງ 50 ຜືນສຳລັບພະນັກງານ, ໂດຍມີກາ"
"ນປັບແຕ່ງໂລໂກ້ໃສ່ຖົງເສື້ອ, ດ້ວຍຈຳນວນເຊັ່ນ: S 5, M 10, L 25, XL 10.\n"
"            </span>"

